$lang['Hexadecimal is a base 16 number system. The numbers 0 through 9 are represented by their corresponding letters (A through F). Numbers from 10 through 15 are represented by two digits, such as 1234 or ABCD. Hexadecimal numbers go beyond these limits, using four characters to represent numbers from 16 through 255.'] = 'Hexadecimal nye xexlẽdzesi 16 ƒe ɖoɖo si wotu ɖe gɔmeɖoanyi dzi. Wotsɔa woƒe ŋɔŋlɔdzesi siwo sɔ (A vaseɖe F) tsi tre ɖi na xexlẽdzesi 0 vaseɖe 9. Wotsɔ xexlẽdzesi eve, abe 1234 alo ABCD ene, tsi tre ɖi na xexlẽdzesi siwo tso 10 va ɖo 15. Xexlẽdzesi siwo nye hexadecimal la yi ŋgɔ wu seɖoƒe siawo, wozãa ŋɔŋlɔdzesi ene tsɔ tsi tre ɖi na xexlẽdzesi siwo tso 16 va ɖo 255.';
